body_html:
@ybsave TensorFlow Debugger (tfdbg) is known to have issues in version 1.0.x on Windows. See issue #7615. Can you try the latest release candidate, namely 1.1.0rc0?

Also beware that the debug_pb2.py file is not an essential feature of tfdbg. It is related to something still under development.

body:
@ybsave TensorFlow Debugger (tfdbg) is known to have issues in version 1.0.x on Windows. See issue https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/7615. Can you try the latest release candidate, namely 1.1.0rc0?

Also beware that the debug_pb2.py file is not an essential feature of tfdbg. It is related to something still under development.
